hed D'Artagnan to find the other musketeers: Cromwell has overthrown the English king, so Mazarin fears revolt, particularly from the popular Beaufort. Porthos, bored with riches and wanting a title, signs on, but Aramis, an abbé, and Athos, a brawler raising an intellectual son, assist Beaufort in secret. When they fail to halt Beaufort's escape from prison, the musketeers are expendable, and Mazarin sends them to London to rescue Charles I. They are also pursued by Justine, the avenging daughter of Milady de Winter, their enemy 20 years ago. They must escape England, avoid Justine, serve the Queen, and secure Beauford's political reforms.","genre_ids":[35,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.9464,"vote_count":150,"poster_path":"/5KP0TNYT2yH1yo7sfV5hQWQ4qWA.jpg","release_date":"1989-04-12","vote_average":6.2,"backdrop_path":"/wDPdVRi8li7ElkwGVD2RoTp9ypx.jpg","original_title":"The Return of the Musketeers","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":852997,"adult":false,"title":"Friend Sister","video":false,"overview":"Jung Tae is living with his girlfriend Young Ji. His friend Min Ho ends up living with Jung Tae and despite the fact that Young Ji doesn't like this situation, Min Ho who is shameless soon gets used to living together. Then one day, another woman appears at home, Jung Tae's former lover and younger step-sister In Hye. Her appearance leaves Jung Tae in great confusion, followed by a sex scandal between four feisty men and women.","genre_ids":[10749],"popularity":0.4457,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/dl19gxIvXrwHRfesHjjVYeGjbut.jpg","release_date":"2021-01-25","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/oT4419btsJfldr53kxQtYKQ8wAj.jpg","original_title":"친구 여동생","original_language":"ko"},{"id":853033,"adult":false,"title":"Adultery Alumni Association 2","video":false,"overview":"Hye Jin, Hee Kyung, and Han Hee who are among the high school alumni. They met at the alumni meeting and heard that the male alumni who did not have a chance to study during